dataset.description:
This data set provides measured crack extensions of each test crack orientation; circumferential, mill-line, and longitudinal, as outlined in Assessment of Emerging Metallic Structures Technologies through Test and Analysis of Fuselage Structure: Test Panel 1, DOT/FAA/TC-21/25, https://rosap.ntl.bts.gov/view/dot/5784.





The Full-Scale Aircraft Structural Test Evaluation and Research (FASTER) facility is capable of testing full scale curved-panel specimens under conditions represetnative of those seen by an aircraft in actual operation. The data obtained from tests is used to support and validate analytical models being developed by the FAA to predict the residual strength of fuselage structure.

References: 15-CRDA-0310, DOT/FAA/TC-21/25, https://rosap.ntl.bts.gov/view/dot/5784
dataset.title: Arconic Panel 1 Crack Extension Data
